    "body": "Works for me:\n\n``` python\nIn [1]: dtype=np.dtype([('firstname','U10'),('lastname','U10'),('age','int32'), ('gender', 'U1')])\n\nIn [2]: dt = np.array([('Jean','Grey',18,'F'),('Logan', 'Howlett', 33,'M')], dtype=dtype)\n\nIn [3]: pd.DataFrame(dt)\nOut[3]: \n  firstname lastname  age gender\n0      Jean     Grey   18      F\n1     Logan  Howlett   33      M\n\nIn [4]: pd.DataFrame.from_records(dt)\nOut[4]: \n  firstname lastname  age gender\n0      Jean     Grey   18      F\n1     Logan  Howlett   33      M\n\n```\n"
